fields.label: Google Maps API Key
fields.name: google_maps_api_key
fields.instructions: In order use of the Google Maps JavaScript API, you must first register a valid API key. To obtain an API key, please follow Google’s Get an API Key instructions. The Google Maps field requires the following APIs; Maps JavaScript API, Geocoding API and Places API.
